# Data & model artifacts: intentionally COMMITTED (not gitignored) so
# the repo works out-of-the-box for anyone browsing/cloning it, without
# requiring a full pipeline run first. All file sizes here are small
# (largest is ~2.5MB for careflow.db) - this decision would need
# revisiting if the dataset or models were much larger, or if this were
# a production repo rather than a portfolio project.
# data/raw/*.csv
# models_saved/*.json
# models_saved/*.pt
# careflow.db

# Generated figures are intentionally NOT ignored - they're small PNGs
# used directly in README.md so the project is browsable on GitHub
# without anyone needing to clone and run the full pipeline first.
